{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_02_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 恋をどう表現する？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――初レッスンから数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days after the first practice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\nお疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚{user}-san.\nHello.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "廊下や階段でみんなぐったりしてたが\n何かあったのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw the others in the hallways‚ looking exhausted.\nWhat’s going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.166666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ……\nちょっとみんなに協力してもらってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe….\nI asked them to help out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "その……\nこ、恋について勉強するために、いろいろと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s‚ er…\ndoing some research into love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなに頼ろうと思って\n今日はずっと聞いて回ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I tracked down the other members of\nMoon Tempest and interviewed them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとすずちゃんは照れて逃げちゃったので\n追いかけて聞き出すのに苦労しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan and Suzu-chan were embarrassed and tried to flee‚\nso it took quite a bit of effort to catch them and get them to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さらりと凄いことを言ったな……\nそりゃ問い詰めたら逃げるだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ you really went all-in…\nI’m not surprised they tried to flee…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんはいろいろと話してくれたんですけど\n途中から猫とかドーナツの話に脱線して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan was happy to talk‚\nbut the conversation soon veered off into cats and donuts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんとも芽衣らしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんは話を振ったとたんにスイッチが入っちゃって\n沢山話してくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I brought up the topic to Nagisa-chan‚ it was like a switch flipped‚\nand she just wouldn’t stop talking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666667347863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "でも……恋を学びたいなら\n映画を一緒に観ようって言い出して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At her suggestion‚\nwe watched a movie together to learn more about love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも恋の感覚を理解したくて、何度も映画を止めて\n解説してもらったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was trying to understand the feeling of love‚\nso I kept pausing the movie and asking her to explain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だから渚までダウンしてるのか……\nそれで、何か成果はあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why Nagisa is exhausted as well…\nWell… did you get any results?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "はい\n……と、言っていいか分からないんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\n…Well‚ actually‚ I’m not 100% sure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、恋への憧れはあっても経験は\nないみたいだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone I talked to has had dreams about love‚\nbut none of them have actual experience with romantic relationships.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ\nそれぞれ恋に抱くイメージみたいなものがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why everyone has\ntheir own ideas about love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いているうちに、私なりに恋をどう表現すれば\nいいかが……ちょっとだけ分かった気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As I listened to them‚\nI began to feel like I had an idea of how to express love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、ちょっとだけですけどね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s just an idea at this stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "ですから\n{user}さんに見ていてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I wanted {user}-san\nto see with your own eyes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "私が……どんな風に変われるのかを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "how I’ve changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……分かった\n楽しみにしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… alright.\nI look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミュージカル本番当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of the musical performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、貴方様は……\nわたくしのことを、どう思っていらっしゃるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dear‚ oh‚ my dear…\nWhat do you think of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "わたくしは、朝起きた時も、お茶会をする時も\n夜眠りに就く時も、考えるのは貴方のことばかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I wake up in the morning‚ when I look out the window‚\nwhen I close my eyes at night‚ all I can think of is you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "残りのレッスンは同行出来なかったが……\n驚いたな、別人じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t make it to the rest of her rehearsals‚\nbut it’s like she’s a completely different person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "主人公に寄り添う仕草も、表情も、声のトーンも……\n最初の稽古の時と段違いだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way she gets close to the protagonist‚ her expression‚ the tone of her voice….\nThere’s a world of difference from the first rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "わたくしばかり貴方様のことを考えているのは……\nとっても寂しいですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ how lonely it feels‚ that you’re in my heart‚\nbut I’m not in yours…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季の演じる女性が見せる普段の姿とのギャップに）\n（周りの観客も息を呑んで見惚れている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The contrast between Saki’s acting and the way)\n(she normally carries herself captivates the audience.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.501985677083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "わたくしは……貴方様にとってなんなのでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me‚ please… what am I to you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.333333333331,
          "startTime": 162.33333333333334
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.333333333331,
