      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 172.133333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n見てくれてましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san. Is it that time already?\nHow was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。小悪魔というか、魔性というか……\n沙季があんな風に演じられるなんて驚いた。見違えたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn’t miss it for the world. It was astounding how you pulled off that…\nhow to put it… that enchanting‚ almost seductive aura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 186.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "本当に恋する淑女がそこにいるみたいだった\nそれもこれも恋について研究したおかげだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like you were really in love.\nAll that research on love seems to have paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "よかった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so glad to hear that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、あれだけ研究しても\nまだ恋については分からないことばかりなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ even after all that research‚\nthere’s still so much I don’t understand about love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、相手を本当に好きだったとしたら……とか\nいろいろなことを想像しながら演じたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I played my role by imagining what I would do\nif I was really in love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あの拍手を聞いただろう？\n沙季の想いはしっかりお客さんに伝わったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You heard the applause‚ didn’t you?\nYou really communicated your feelings to the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 216.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_03-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、凄く嬉しかったです\n今までやってきた努力が通じなくて、悩んで悩んで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so glad to hear that.\nI was so perplexed when the hard work I put in came up empty.",
        "id": ""
