      "text": "そんな中で、頑張る方向性を変えたら\n今まで知らなかった自分に出会えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I explored a different way of working hard‚ however‚\nI found a side of myself that I never knew existed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
